a 7 segment 4 digit module and 16 leds for IO testing
Pins for a module:
1.5V GND (POWER)
2.CLK RESET READY (Clock signals)
3. !TEST (WAIT instruction)
4.ADDR[0..19] DATA[0..15] (for Address and Data bus)
5.!IORD !IOWR !MRD !MWR for io and memory input output
6.!BHE for addr and databus control signal
7.HOLD and HLDA for hold request and hold permit
8.NMI INTR and !INTA for Non maskable interrupt,Interrupt request and Interrupt permit

